name: The Weed Thief Rat with Laser Eyes!
description: One day, I noticed my bag of marijuana was missing, so I started looking and found a rat that was smoking my joint. He told me he had stolen and hidden my marijuana bag, the fabric of which had been made from Mondrian's soul. And on top of that, he said he wouldn't even give me a drag on that cigarette. I know the rat also stole my mushrooms, got mad and developed lasers in his eyes, and destroyed my house. But I have a plan to get rid of him. I'll tell you later.
